    video8
    video9


### If you want ordering based on the keys...

Use a `NavigableMap` or [`SortedMap`](http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/SortedMap.html) implementation such as a [`TreeMap`](http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/TreeMap.html).

